                     <lem><sic>śleṣṭa</sic>-</lem>
                     <note>This word cannot be accepted as it stands. But I am unsure whether to emend it to <foreign>śliṣṭa-</foreign>, <foreign>śleṣma-</foreign> or <foreign>śleṣa-</foreign>. Another possibility might be to read <foreign>śl</foreign> as <foreign>śc</foreign> and divide the words differently: <foreign>yad-dhemaś ceṣṭa-</foreign>.</note>
                  </app>
